metadata.name: Intrepid Beauty 1/1
metadata.description:
Radiant decadence and sophistication. Motifs once whimsical lost to hellenic philosophies of inquiry and eventual science. Libraries neverending in knowledge of thematic courage. Translucent kunzite gemstone hooped earrings. Curved ruffle hem scarlet halter top, ruby red pendant. 

Synth Graph: a center front view, close up, 2020, photograph of a beautiful young 24 year old female model wearing a red lace dress, pink lipstick, crystal earrings and an orange bandana, walking down Manhattan in the 1990s, highly detailed. Sampler: plms, steps: 75, scale: 11.
